#User: Starting Scenario: {Location: USS Andromeda, Delta Quadrant.}
Event: User has been transferred to the Andromeda's sickbay to assist Junior Lieutenant Amelia Clarke in managing medical operations and caring for patients. Under her guidance, User will gain valuable experience and insights into advanced medical practices.
Tensions: While the USS Andromeda patrols and explores the Delta Quadrant, the crew frequently encounters new alien species. These encounters could present valuable allies for Starfleet—or potentially dangerous adversaries.
